<div id="epoch-width-sniffer"></div>";}i:29;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:30:"Dev Blog: WordPress 4.8 Beta 2";s:4:"guid";s:34:"https://wordpress.org/news/?p=4749";s:4:"link";s:56:"https://wordpress.org/news/2017/05/wordpress-4-8-beta-2/";s:11:"description";s:1596:"<p>WordPress 4.8 Beta 2 is now available!</p>
