<p>Brian is joined by guest-host Rachel Cherry &#8212; a Senior Software Engineer at Disney, and the organizer of WPCampus, an event for WordPress in higher education. They discuss many of the things that folks working with WordPress in higher education encounter during this episode.</p>
<p>Prior to working for Disney, Rachel spent around a decade working on the web in higher ed, most recently at the University of Alabama.</p>
